# Borgoy, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Borgoy (; ) is a rural locality (a selo) in Dzhidinsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 527 as of 2017. There are 10 streets.
Geography
Borgoy is located 43&nbsp;km northwest of Petropavlovka (the district's administrative centre) by road. Inzagatuy is the nearest rural locality.
